OL,3,C'Drowned' baby had dry hair, murder
OL,4,Ctrial hears
OL,6,FA "murdered" baby whom a teacher
OL,7,Fclaimed accidentally drowned in a bath
OL,8,Fwas not wet and had dry hair, a court
OL,9,Fhas heard.
OL,11,FJamie Varley, 37, claims he left his
OL,12,F"happy, smiley, giggly" adopted 13-
OL,13,Fmonth-old son, Preston Davey, in the
OL,14,Fbath for two or three minutes and
OL,15,Freturned to find him submerged - an
OL,16,Faccount prosecutors allege is made up
OL,17,Fto cover his sexual abuse and murder
OL,18,Fof the child.
OL,26,@tD@AOUtD@WO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/8
