PN,39502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1780600264
OL,3,C'Drowned' baby had dry hair, murder
OL,4,Ctrial hears
OL,6,FHis partner and co-accused, John
OL,7,FMcGowan-Fazakerley, 32, told Preston
OL,8,FCrown Court when he returned home to
OL,9,FBlackpool from work in financial
OL,10,Fsales, Varley, a former high school
OL,11,Fhead of year, was trying to revive
OL,12,Ftheir stricken son.
OL,14,FProsecutor Peter Wright KC, in cross-
OL,15,Fexamination of McGowan-Fazakerley,
OL,16,Fsaid: "Well, his hair was not wet?"
OL,18,FMcGowan-Fazakerley said: "I can't
OL,19,Frecall it being wet. I remember it
OL,20,Fbeing sort of quite tight locks.
OL,21,FPreston was not wet, put it that way."
OL,26,@xD@GOUxD@cO]zD@ZOU}D@fO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/8
