OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1780600264
OL,3,C'Drowned' baby had dry hair, murder
OL,4,Ctrial hears
OL,6,FEarlier the court heard Preston, a
OL,7,F"sweet and bubbly" baby boy, was
OL,8,Fadopted by the couple in April 2023.
OL,10,FBut prosecutors allege, during the
OL,11,Ffour months Preston was living at
OL,12,Ftheir Blackpool home before he was
OL,13,Frushed to hospital unresponsive, on 27
OL,14,FJuly, he was routinely ill-treated,
OL,15,Fhad indecent images and videos taken
OL,16,Fof him, and was sexually abused and
OL,17,Fphysically assaulted.
OL,26,@oD@AOUoD@RO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/8
