PN,39507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1780600264
OL,3,C'Drowned' baby had dry hair, murder
OL,4,Ctrial hears
OL,6,FThe cause of Preston's death was found
OL,7,Fto be acute upper airways obstruction
OL,8,Fby either smothering or an object or
OL,9,Fobjects inserted into his mouth.
OL,11,FPreston was used as a "plaything" for
OL,12,Fthe "amusement" of the defendants, Mr
OL,13,FWright told jurors.
OL,26,@sD@WOUsD@aO]tD@EOUtD@OO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/8
